FRC2Remote - FRC2 中的 接口
The FRC2Remote class provides a Java RMI-compliant interface to the M-functions from the files: E:\\Dropbox\\wds\\yanwang\\xunruiCodes\\matlab\\Java2\\NonUniformFlow.m The dispose() method must be called on a FRC2Remote instance when it is no longer needed to ensure that native resources allocated by this class are properly freed, and the server-side proxy is unexported.
